@@ -314,6 +314,18 @@ 5. Diff options						*diff-options*
 
 Also see |'diffopt'| and the "diff" item of |'fillchars'|.
 
+					    *diff-slow* *diff_translations*
+For very long lines, the diff syntax highlighting might be considerably slow,
+especially since it tries to match all different kind of localisations. To
+disable localisations and speed up the syntax highlighting, set the global
+variable g:diff_translations to zero: >
+
+    let g:diff_translations=0
+<
+After setting this variable, Reload the syntax script: >
+
+    set syntax=diff
+<
 
 FINDING THE DIFFERENCES					*diff-diffexpr*
 
